    },
    {
      "id": "eq_6639",
      "raw": "Pf(Omega) = (1/(2^m m!)) epsilon_{a1...a_{2m}} Omega^{a_1 a_2} ^ ... ^ Omega^{a_{2m-1} a_{2m}}",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "where Omega is the curvature 2-form of the TANGENT BUNDLE. The Pfaffian of a 2m-form valued so(2m) matrix:",
      "session": "21c",
