      "error_note": "",
      "severity": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "eq_6640",
      "raw": "# For m=4 (8-manifold):",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "The Pfaffian of a 2m-form valued so(2m) matrix: Pf(Omega) = (1/(2^m m!)) epsilon_{a1...a_{2m}} Omega^{a_1 a_2} ^ ... ^ Omega^{a_{2m-1} a_{2m}}",
      "session": "21c",
      "source_file": "tier0-computation\\s21c_gb_debug4.py",
      "line": 216,
      "existing_latex": "",
